{"tid":331483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地越禁　人民越醒覺不自由","createTime":"2017-07-22T08:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T02:30:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6572e07895dcd64843708e9af941347abf1db09","tid":331483,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20097621&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20097621%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170722&d=b9yxPpJKNKz6P7TRKkHuap4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ea461c06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20097621%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170722&h=d04dd674\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20097621&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170722</a><br />\n<br />\n內地越禁　人民越醒覺不自由<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170722/large/a1602a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170722%2Flarge%2Fa1602a.gif&h=77233872&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在紐約的華裔維權人士要求中國政府拆除網絡長城防火牆。<br />\n<br />\n內地為政治原因翻牆的民眾其實不多，有人為聯繫國外的客戶朋友；有人為了國外的新知；有人想玩遊戲；有人為追星&hellip;&hellip;當局越是禁止，人民越醒覺自己並不自由。封鎖可以激發好奇，恐懼卻同時令探索卻步，最終哪種力量會更強，我們拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n影響升學社交<br />\n<br />\n多家VPN一夜倒閉，網民給了的錢打水漂，當局並沒有走出來解釋，到底翻牆有甚麽錯？到底外國網站有甚麽「非法信息」讓中共如此緊張，要掩住國民的眼睛？有說是近期郭文貴大爆中共高層貪腐黑幕，有說是劉曉波病逝的信息。但這些並非廣大國內民眾所最關心，對於封VPN，目前看見最多的抱怨是，國外的文獻查不了、影響入學進程、阻斷社交、不能使用國外的技術。<br />\n隨着科技進步，沒有不透風的牆，當局再多網絡警察也沒法完全監控14億人，但殺雞儆猴確有一定功效。「翻牆就會被請喝茶，好緊張啊！」有網民表示，還是不翻牆了。卻也有勇者說：「派出所的接待能力也是有限的嘛，讓不翻就不翻認輸了。再說喝過一次就脫敏了嘛。」有人調侃以後翻牆軟件可以取名「愛國」，大家就可以公開問： 「誰有愛國軟件分享一下」；或取名「禁止」，大家就可以直接問「誰知道怎麼禁止啊？」<br />\n《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t中共封殺　翻牆App「陣亡」製作人被捕　網民無法上Gmail　YouTube<br />\n兩岸要聞 8小時前"},{"pid":"6151674c27e6fc04bc4f8fb9b4b8999fa70c4319","tid":331483,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:21:58.000Z","msg":"鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aad10c36d575b8eaa119e3a99fc638b09a25b21","tid":331483,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:23:47.000Z","msg":"好想睇下支那五毛有咩反應"},{"pid":"95447d0306ec7d4e61077243e687da43b31e9248","tid":331483,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"得個幾丁友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0da7a7963e67cffaf3b71377b8c0b0347bcd33","tid":331483,"uid":42764,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:01:01.000Z","msg":"醒覺有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇死佢地唔會反抗，連大饑荒都無人賣命，點會為VPN呢啲事而反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ef368808810847202b631fa5842a926069ac42","tid":331483,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:02:00.000Z","msg":"又話大陸唔比集會<br />\n仲唔拉？"},{"pid":"89e1a54481dc545ecf758e1b738442ffcd8f2e98","tid":331483,"uid":531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想睇下支那五毛有咩反應</blockquote><br />\n五毛係官方放出所以冇影響"},{"pid":"d0201bdfe1341db6519cdf2010b69fe6e9b88503","tid":331483,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:10:16.000Z","msg":"千其咪"},{"pid":"df1d266fde4cd567de7fc3a50878d9f4f9f7991e","tid":331483,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想睇下支那五毛有咩反應</blockquote><br />\n近排少左好多五毛回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93033c9819c16245b988e5c6bb9b39a8147d67b","tid":331483,"uid":10692,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:23:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e701707325f6b98bba807c3e5c3728d3138d32d","tid":331483,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"你無做錯怕乜封牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5610ee933967f35dba47d9a50cb5e834f6dac96b","tid":331483,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7720e6c9551f6d84dbd2ab80825bcdab166f7339","tid":331483,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"支持國家政策"},{"pid":"48e764525ee9bc899766746ba50663fe33252aff","tid":331483,"uid":12362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"在<span style=\"color: red;\">紐約</span>的華裔維權人士要求中國政府拆除網絡長城防火牆。"},{"pid":"6989c6b5e28e58b09d233dc9d64ffca16bd25dd9","tid":331483,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在<span style=\"color: red;\">紐約</span>的華裔維權人士要求中國政府拆除網絡長城防火牆。</blockquote><br />\n隔住個大西洋再隔住個歐亞大陸<br />\n向中國政府施壓<br />\n中共表示好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbcbf2773372091f837aefbe76a4651afc1828d","tid":331483,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"話少左五毛果d都弱撚智 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n五毛係國家比錢當然會提供埋翻牆渠道比佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208deabd3adb893b847e8731cb2ce5d5ac85288c","tid":331483,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:16:21.000Z","msg":"2027年<br />\n<br />\n習爺爺搖搖頭，「不礙事，你們知道現在國際上有很多人把社會主義當作敵人，不斷給我們制造麻煩，你們是祖國的未來，你們的事情便是國家的事情，是頭等大事。」我們都激動了，眼裏噙著淚花。<br />\n<br />\n多好的習爺爺呀。習爺爺抬頭看看天空說：「如果世界真像這天空這麽安靜就好了，但是就有一些國家，像美國，要搞亂這個世界，他們是罪人。」<br />\n<br />\n說著，習爺爺彎下腰，從花池裏撿出一顆石子，然後看著天空說：「該死的美國佬。」說著他把石子奮力向上一擲。很快就見空中一顆衛星突然爆發出耀眼的強光，然後就墜落下來。"},{"pid":"2170b1237ffd3ea6acd340ab564276ad0a635423","tid":331483,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:17:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fd1c4e619c332c97b945c3b4c5bf247b4a66de3","tid":331483,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T01:54:51.000Z","msg":"你諗下好啦。大陸仲有大把人覺得，自己有野食有份工，係全因為共產黨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋，佢地都覺得自己好撚自由，可以講咩，睇咩都得，去邊又得etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d4d0a1c440502411f2deef5c317b4b6bad7a03","tid":331483,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"不自由又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢班人最好唔好自由出黎搞亂世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5e26fbf0d04eabb68996da20b4e1e3fa4987c4","tid":331483,"uid":9483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:02:40.000Z","msg":"小熊維尼都禁啦<br />\n中共真係無野做唔出"},{"pid":"97a0971e9fbda5a172c5ab32c695c782c5f92006","tid":331483,"uid":42977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你諗下好啦。大陸仲有大把人覺得，自己有野食有份工，係全因為共產黨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a